item.title: Rebound MTB App
item.description: The Rebound MTB App Link to heading Part 1: The beta release Link to heading For the past forever I’ve been studying with the Open University, working towards a Bachelor’s degree in Software Engineering and after all that time the end is in sight!. To complete the degree I have to undertake a significant project, so I’ve teamed up with the guys at Rebound to build a mobile application to support them.
